Phytochemical constituents were determined by subjecting the extracts to qualitative analysis using standard procedures (
 Harborne, 1998; 
 Edeoga et al., 2005; 
 Sofowora, 2006). Quantitative estimation of the phytoconstituents of phenols and tannins were determined by spectrophotometric method (
 Krishnaiah et al., 2009), while quantification of saponins, alkaloids, flavonoids and glycosides were estimated using procedure as reported by 
 Harborne (1998).
